Check plugin for system sensors
Copyright:  2012, Tony Yarusso
Auther:     Tony Yarusso <tonyyarusso@gmail.com>
License:    BSD <http://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.php>

Options:
    -h | --help
           Display this help text
    -V | --version
           Display the version of this script
    -s | --sensor <sensor>
           Set which sensor to query
    -t | --type <type>
           Set the sensor type (eg. Temperature or Fan
    -w | --warning <level>
           The high sensor reading to trigger a warning state
    -c | --critical <level>
           The high sensor reading to trigger a critical state
    -W | --low-warning <level>
           The low sensor reading to trigger a warning state
    -C | --low-critical <level>
           The low sensor reading to trigger a critical state
